issues.description: The Virtual Connect throughput statistics configuration is different from the OneView logical interconnect group utilization sampling configuration. The VC sample count is 300, while OneView sample count is 300, And VC SampleInterval is 60, while OneView Sample Interval is 300.
issues.recommendation: Modify the OneView interval between samples and total number of samples on the logical interconnect group such that the resulting sample collection rate and total sample history are equivalent to the Virtual Connect configuration. Alternatively modify the Virtual Connect configuration to match the OneView configuration.
